Package: myproteomicsR
Title: Statistical Analysis of DIA Phosphoproteomics Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Marie", "Locard-Paulet", email = "author@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for loading, filtering, and performing differential abundance
    analysis on Spectronaut DIA proteomics and phosphoproteomics reports using
    limma. Includes functions for quality control plots, missing value
    imputation, and export of results to Excel.
